      <section name='tammy'>

         <para number='1' comment='tammy match hello'>
         Tammy smiles her brightest smile and says "Welcome to Universal Salvage. We are equal opportunity employers and the friendliest company in The Rift.  How may I help you today?"
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='tammy match work/job'>
         Tammy looks you over carefully "In order to work for Universal Salvage you will need a local reference. Please state the name of your personal reference here on Penance". She waits with fingers poised over her keyboard for you to give her a name.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='tammy match joey'>
         Tammy brightens "Ah.. of course!  Well now let me see... " She taps away at her keyboard and scans the monitor "I do have a vacancy in the maintenance section." Tammy thrusts a form in your direction. "To accept the post please READ FORM."
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='tammy match penance'>
         "Oh it's not as bad as it sounds." Tammy smiles "We have some benefits that visitors don't get to see." She leans forward and lowers her voice "You know this place was already here when we arrived.  The company just enlarged the facilities. Nobody actually knows who was here before or who joined the three asteroids that make up Penance."
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='tammy match pay/wage'>
         Tammy pulls up your records on her computer "well now, %s, you'll have to start at a pay rate that is comensurate with your skills.  I'm afraid in your case that would be Galactic minimum wage."
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='tammy match benefits'>
         Tammy smiles, "We have quite a few facilities here, and believe it or not, we have a lovely park in the middle of Beta Rock"
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='tammy nomatch'>
         Tammy gets a fixed smile "I'm sorry.  Please come back when you are looking for work and have a local reference.  Have a nice day"
         </para>

